_sText:
This is a map I have wanted to edit for quite some time. The original was always a popular map, but it was too small and not enough hiding places/props etc.

I have extended the map all the way to the front yard and added a heap of new places to hide and props to blend in with.

[Prop List - Click Here](http://dumptext.com/WLTWEU0c "Prop List")
